        "title": "What makes us different",
        "content": "<p>We understand that these pieces aren’t just jewellery – they’re symbols of love, commitment, and the moments that matter most.</p><p>As proud members of the <strong>National Association of Jewellers</strong>, we hold ourselves to the highest standards of quality and care.</p><p>Our commitment to excellence begins with <strong>18ct gold vermeil</strong>, which is 25 times thicker than standard gold plating. We plate all our silver with<strong> rhodium</strong>, one of the rarest and most valuable metals, and apply an <strong>anti-tarnish e-coating</strong> for added protection and water resistance.</p><p>Each of our diamond simulants is meticulously hand-set, reflecting our dedication to craftsmanship.</p><p>We use ECO Packaging which is FSC® certified... and if all this wasn't enough, we offer a 2 Year Warranty for peace of mind.</p>",
