        },
        "richtext_Vw8bcN": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Every day, we pinch ourselves to believe it's real. It's an incredible honour that each of you chooses our promise rings to symbolise your special commitments. </p><p>Knowing that our rings are part of your meaningful moments fills us with gratitude. </p><p>Thank you for trusting us with something so personal and important. <strong>It means the world to us.</strong></p>"
