    "image_with_text_J9HyfR": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_tY4aBn": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "We started with a question:"
          }
        },
        "heading_hrNkLe": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "What does it really mean to make a promise?",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_EMPPNH": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>And why hadn’t the jewellery industry evolved to reflect the depth and diversity of the promises we make today?</p><p>Traditionally, promise rings were tied to romantic milestones. And while we’ll <em>always </em>celebrate those love stories – they’re at the heart of so much of what we do – we also knew there was more. Because in real life, promises aren’t one-size-fits-all.</p><p>They can be quiet and steady. Fierce and full of hope. A vow to begin again. A bond between best friends. A reminder to keep going.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "subheading_tY4aBn",
        "heading_hrNkLe",
        "richtext_EMPPNH"
      ],
