        },
        "heading_thQmra": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "So we created it",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_rQ3W73": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>At The Promise Co., we’re here to redefine what a promise ring can be. To move beyond tradition and make space for the full spectrum of what it means to care, to commit, and to believe in something – or someone.</p><p>This is jewellery that honours all kinds of promises. The big ones. The quiet ones. The ones you share and the ones you keep just for yourself.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
